===Transitive phrasal verb===
to '''pin (something) down''';
#to [[attach]] or [[secure]] with [[pin]]s
#:'''''Pin down''' the tablecloth, so it doesn't blow away in the breeze.''
#{{idiom}} to [[identify]] something (e.g. a decision or plan) [[clear]]ly or [[specific]]ly
#:''Something is wrong, but I can't '''pin it down'''.''
#(''idiomatic'') to get a [[firm]] [[answer]] from someone
#:''Let's try to '''pin him down''' on a price.''

